These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: salsa, techno
1. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of techno##1
2. the fan of techno is not to the right of the fan of techno##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2  |
| Music-Genre   | techno | salsa |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, superhero
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is not to the left of the person watching superhero movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | documentary |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-3::.
2 different pets are kept: ferret, bird
1. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the owner of the bird##5
2. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
3. the owner of the ferret is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |
| Pet   | ferret | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-4::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, van
1. the person driving the quad-bike is not to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##8
2. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |
| Transport   | quad-bike | van |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-5::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, drawing
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##8
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |   2    |
| Hobby   | drawing | board-games |

